    <name>Bulk Renamer</name>
    <summary>Rename multiple files according to one or more rules</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Rename multiple files by applying on or more rules to the original name or to a new basename</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Add an index number with a chosen starting point and digits as a prefix or suffix</li>
            <li>Add a date (current, creation or modification) as a prefix or suffix</li>
            <li>Add or replace text</li>
        </ul>
        <p>A chosed separator may be inserted together with the new text.</p>
    </description>
