                <p>Initial release</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use original name or a new constant name as a basis for renaming</li>
                    <li> Add a number sequence, date or text before or after the basename</li>
                    <li>Choose an arbitrary separator for new text</li>
                    <li>Replace a specified part of the name with other text</li>
